## 6. Diagrama de Casos de Uso

```plantuml
@startuml
left to right direction
actor "Tester / Automatizador" as User

package "PYJX2 System" {
    usecase "Configurar Entorno (Setup)" as UC_Setup
    usecase "Sincronizar Evidencias (Sync)" as UC_Sync
    usecase "Cifrar Credenciales" as UC_Config
    usecase "Visualizar Manual (Docs)" as UC_Docs
}

User --> UC_Setup
User --> UC_Sync
User --> UC_Config
User --> UC_Docs

UC_Setup ..> UC_Config : <<include>> (opcional si usa ENC:)
@enduml
```
